pTitle: Trimline Telephone With Memory - Black
rText: I purchased this phone from Home Depot because I wanted to replace my old AT&T Trimline phone which I had it for over 20 years and it is still in working condition except the ringer bell tone does not work. I was searching for this type of phone through various web sites and the prices were anywhere from $17.00 to $23.00 and Home Depot had the cheapest price for around $12.99. This phone works excellent. The only disadvantage is the electronic ringer tone is not loud and my old AT&T Trim line phone that I had for over 20- years had a very loud ringing bell tone. I understand that old is like gold but I am happy with this one.
rTitle: One of the Excellent ATT&T Trimline Telephone
